column5: I'm going down to the fishing show either Sunday or Monday depending on reel fishing plans. I want to check-out some Live Target Lure "in the flesh" so to speak. See any?
is that those realistic looking lure?  he had a booth there.

there was a booth there showing all the colours and the different styles, they have really expanded their product line. They had some new rattlin raps that looked like crayfish that were pretty cool, they also had some shallow running lures that looked like a wake bait that was nice.
we've got all kinds at the tightline booth..stop by and see me.  Todd
:Gonefishing Picked up a couple of the crawfish on friday the natural and the orange brown.They are sure pretty looking and if they don't catch any bass I will mount them on my wall.Just kidding.
Fishing World and Natural Sports both had a good selection.
